  "text": "It has been proven that the statistical data about iris can be used for iris recognition system [CITATION_1] . That is why in our system statistical analysis of iris data is done first. On the iris image the circles are marked at the distance of 5 pixels each as shown in fig. 3 . For every circle marked the above mentioned definitions are calculated. ",
